_sText:
It's time to play the Gungame version of that classic "Chutes And Ladders" game.
We have Chutes, Ladders, a Spinner, some Dice, and 4 Player Pieces on the board.
Except in this version, the players are looking to headshot each other!!!

Note: You can only go DOWN the Chutes but the Ladders are bi-directional.
And the GravPipe in the center only softens the landing.
Also, there are Hidden Teleports - so watch that platform leaping.

~~~ Worm
